5. ComfyUI SAM 3D Body node (pose estimation reference)
------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Upstream:    https://github.com/PozzettiAndrea/ComfyUI-SAM3DBody
   License:     See upstream repository.
   Use here:    The vendored sam_3d_body inference package
                (image2bvh/vendor/sam_3d_body/) was derived from this
                repository. Modifications applied here include:
                  - decoupling from ComfyUI's node infrastructure
                  - exposing a Python-callable inference API
                  - replacing per-person sequential calls with a
                    single batched call
                  - shifting the humanoid thumb mapping by one joint
                    so the proximal-phalanx-onward chain is captured
                BVH writing has been replaced with a pure-Python
                static-pose writer (image2bvh/bvh_writer.py); the
                original Blender-based builder scripts shipped with
                the upstream node are no longer used.

