6. ComfyUI-SAM3DBody_utills (forward-lean correction reference)
------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Upstream:    https://github.com/tori29umai0123/ComfyUI-SAM3DBody_utills
   License:     See upstream repository.
   Use here:    The forward-lean correction algorithm in
                image2bvh/pose.py:apply_lean_correction was ported
                from this repo's
                nodes/processing/process.py:apply_pose_lean_correction_rig.
                The default chain (spine_01 +20°, neck_01 +2°,
                head +2°) and the rig-space rotation math match the
                upstream behaviour.

